              ♦ P R E P A R E  T O  B E  U N L E A S H E D ! ! ♦


                             My Jurassic Farm RIP                           
 ─♦─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────♦─
   Release Date  :  12/03/2015                Protection  :  Steam
   Release Type  :  RIP 12x5.00MB             Company     :  BiP media
 ─♦─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────♦─
   Release Notes:

                                                                            
   At the beginning of the game, all you own is an empty field, a few       
   pennies and a single little compsognathus... You need to feed your       
   compsognathus, take care of it and improve its lifestyle. Well fed       
   with meat, your compsognathus will lay eggs which can then be sold to    
   the Shopkeeper. With this money, you can buy new animals at the          
   Farmers' Market...                                                       
                                                                            
       10 kinds of animals to customize!                                    
       Take care of your animals: food, clean, disease, etc.                
       Many farm improvement to buy and bonuses to collect!                 
                                                                            
                                                                            
                                                                            
   RIPPED: Nothing                                                          
 ─♦─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────♦─
   Install Notes:
         
   1. Unpack the release with WinRAR or equivalent                          
   2. Install by running unl-myjp.exe                                       
   3. Start game with MyJurassicFarm.exe                                    
   4. Enjoy!                                                                
                                                                            
   Remember to support quality games!                                       
                                                                            
 ─♦─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────♦─

     Unleashed salutes all friends of the family, contacts and competition! 

 ─♦─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────♦─
